# Genesis Marketplace - Environment Variables Example
#
# This file documents all environment variables used by the genesis-marketplace application.
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values for local development.

# Currently, this project does not use any environment variables in the codebase.
# It is a Next.js frontend application for the Agent Skill Economy marketplace.

# If you need to add environment variables in the future, follow this pattern:
# VARIABLE_NAME=value_placeholder

# Development
# NODE_ENV=development
